出血がある対象を優先して攻撃
自分の攻撃で対象を倒したなら、精神力が最も低い敵の精神力が15減少。

When this unit defeats the target with an attack, enemy with the lowest SP loses 15 SP.
When this unit defeats the target with an attack, reuse Skill on a different target.
